metadata.name: Children! Get in some sort of a L I N E !!!
metadata.description:
1/1 minted by Mad Monk, Madera del Diablo smart contract, 2023

Own smart contract starts with Beach Blurrr Chapter. 

https://opensea.io/collection/madera-del-diablo  
https://foundation.app/collection/maderadeldiablo

Madera del Diablo is the second part of the Devil's Wood project. The artwork of the first part provided the source material which was worked up with AI. Furthermore additional sources and spot collaborations were (and are) taken up to create variety. Now launching on its own Manifold deployed smart contract, Madera del Diablo consists of short thematic chapters. The project will be minted on various platforms.
